title: Week 6 Studs & Duds + The Impossibles - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/18
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 6! Which surprise performances are a sign of things to come, and which dud performances are the most worrisome for fantasy football going forward? Plus, lots of injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 18th, 2021.
  
 (03:40) - Monday Punday
 (06:00) - NFL News
 (14:45) - Fantasy Studmuffins
 (14:50) - QB Studs
 (18:25) - RB Studs
 (30:10) - WR Studs
 (35:00) - TE Studs
 (38:25) - Fantasy Duds
 (38:30) - QB Duds
 (41:30) - RB Duds
 (44:35) - WR Duds
 (50:35) - TE Duds
